## 4. `App` composition (service container)

`[internal/app.App](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L43-L63)` aggregates persistence, permissions, agent coordination, LSP, and config. Construction in `[app.New](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L65-L118)`:

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  N["app.New"] --> S["session.Service"]
  N --> M["message.Service"]
  N --> H["history.Service"]
  N --> P["permission.Service"]
  N --> C["agent.Coordinator"]
  N --> L["LSPClients map"]
  N --> BG["initLSPClients / checkForUpdates / mcp.Initialize"]
```



Background work started from `[app.New](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L95-L104)`: LSP client init, update checks, MCP initialization.

