## 5. Agent stack (LLM + tools)

**Libraries**: `[charm.land/fantasy](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/go.mod)` for multi-provider LLM; Catwalk for model metadata; tools implement `fantasy.AgentTool`.

```mermaid
flowchart TB
  COO["agent.Coordinator"]
  SA["SessionAgent (sessionAgent)"]
  COO --> SA
  SA --> LM["large/small Model (fantasy.LanguageModel)"]
  SA --> T["[]fantasy.AgentTool"]
  T --> BASH["bash"]
  T --> EDIT["edit / multiedit / write"]
  T --> GREP["grep / glob"]
  T --> FETCH["fetch / web_fetch"]
  T --> MCP["MCP bridge"]
  T --> LSPt["diagnostics / view"]
```




| Component                      | Code                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Coordinator contract           | `[internal/agent/coordinator.go` L44–58](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L44-L58)                                                                                                 |
| Coordinator construction       | `[NewCoordinator](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L74-L82)`                                                                                                                       |
| Session agent + queue / cancel | `[internal/agent/agent.go` L62–97](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/agent.go#L62-L97), `[NewSessionAgent](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/agent.go#L112-L120)` |
