## 11. End-to-end: user message → reply (main TUI)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User / Terminal
  participant T as tui.appModel
  participant A as app.App
  participant C as agent.Coordinator
  participant LLM as LLM provider
  U->>T: key / paste / submit
  T->>A: session / message services
  A->>C: Run(ctx, sessionID, prompt, ...)
  C->>LLM: fantasy agent loop
  LLM-->>C: tokens / tool calls
  C->>A: persist via message.Service
  A-->>T: tea.Msg via pubsub / subscribe
  T-->>U: rendered view (lipgloss / glamour)
```



Coordinator API: `[Coordinator.Run](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L47-L47)`.

